# ── Production build (Vercel, Render static site, etc.) ─────────────────────
# API origin only — no path, no trailing slash. Required when the UI is hosted
# on a different origin than the API (set matching CORS_ORIGINS on the backend).
# VITE_API_URL=https://your-api.onrender.com

# ── Local dev: optional proxy target (default http://localhost:3000) ─────────
# Point at a remote API while still using /api in the browser (avoids CORS during dev).
# VITE_DEV_API_URL=https://your-api.onrender.com

# Local dev with local API: leave both unset; Vite proxies /api → localhost:3000.
